==经济==
{{Asof|2018}}，泰国交通部投资19亿[[泰铢|泰铢]]兴建勿洞国际机场。该机场原订2020年6月启用，<ref>{{cite news |title=Govt plans DMK-Betong flight roster |url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/general/1680140/govt-plans-dmk-betong-flight-roster |accessdate=19 May 2019 |work=Bangkok Post |date=19 May 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Sritama |first1=Suchat |title=Better days around the bend |url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/special-reports/1529118/better-days-around-the-bend |accessdate=27 August 2018 |work=Bangkok Post |date=27 August 2018}}</ref>但由于[[新冠肺炎疫情|新冠肺炎疫情]]影响预计延迟至2021年全面竣工启用，目前只开放参观。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kwongwah.com.my/20200622/%e5%8b%bf%e6%b4%9e%e5%9b%bd%e9%99%85%e6%9c%ba%e5%9c%ba-%e6%88%90%e6%96%b0%e6%89%93%e5%8d%a1%e5%9c%b0%e7%82%b9/|title=勿洞国际机场 成新打卡地点|website=光华网|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817125959/https://www.kwongwah.com.my/20200622/%E5%8B%BF%E6%B4%9E%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA-%E6%88%90%E6%96%B0%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该机场每小时将有300趟航班，每年将有100万乘客，为该县带来30亿泰铢。[[皇雀航空|皇雀航空]]、[[曼谷航空|曼谷航空]]和马来西亚的[[飞萤航空|飞萤航空]]有计划飞到勿洞。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Nanuam|first1=Wassana|title=Betong airport runway will be extended, says army chief |url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/1707590/betong-airport-runway-will-be-extended-says-army-chief |accessdate=5 July 2019 |work=Bangkok Post |date=5 July 2019}}</ref>

