==旅游景点==
*友谊村地道（Piyamit Tunnel）曾是[[马来亚共产党|马来亚共产党]]的据点，也是防范空袭及储藏粮食的基地，1976年建成，约1公里长。现在是一个博物馆。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tourismthailand.org/Attraction/piyamit-tunnel|title=Piyamit Tunnel|website=www.tourismthailand.org|access-date=2020-07-17|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717045355/https://www.tourismthailand.org/Attraction/piyamit-tunnel|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*Talay Mok Aiyoeweng云海，{{convert|2,038|ft|abbr=on}}，10月至3月几乎每一天早晨可看见。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thailandtourismdirectory.go.th/en/info/attraction/detail/itemid/933 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-17 |archive-date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717062151/https://thailandtourismdirectory.go.th/en/info/attraction/detail/itemid/933 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*其他景点包括世界最大邮箱（约{{convert|9|m|abbr=on}}高<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thailandtourismdirectory.go.th/zh/info/attraction/detail/itemid/3734 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-17 |archive-date=2020-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720011408/https://thailandtourismdirectory.go.th/zh/info/attraction/detail/itemid/3734 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）、泰南最大佛像、木雕观音菩萨庙、热水湖、万花园等。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.airbnb.co.in/experiences/1076180|title=Holiday Lets, Homes, Experiences & Places|website=Airbnb}}</ref>

